msgstr "Fela tóma hluta"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/page.phtml:80
msgid "Hide more options"
msgstr "Fela fleiri valkosti"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/config.phtml:65
msgid "Hide the PNG export button"
msgstr "Fela PNG útflutningshnappinn"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/config.phtml:56
msgid "Hide the SVG export button"
msgstr "Fela SVG útflutningshnappinn"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/config.phtml:102
msgid ""
"How much of each place hierarchy is shown in chart arcs (full name, or only "
"the lowest 1–3 levels). Users toggle place visibility on/off in the chart "
"form."
msgstr ""
"Hversu mikið af hverri staðarstigskipan er sýnt í bogum töflunnar (fullt "
"nafn eða aðeins lægstu 1–3 stigin). Notendur kveikja/slökkva á sýnileika "
"staða í töfluformi."

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/form/display.phtml:59
msgid ""
"Images are only shown if the arc segment is wide enough. Images for "
"descendants are not yet available."
msgstr ""
"Myndir birtast aðeins ef bogahlutinn er nógu breiður. Myndir af afkomendum "
"eru ekki enn tiltækar."

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/page.phtml:41
msgid "Individual"
msgstr "Einstaklingur"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/form/details.phtml:34
msgid ""
"Inserts the GEDCOM NICK value in quotes between the given names and the "
"surname (e.g. Martin \"Chalky\" White). Mirrors the legacy webtrees "
"behaviour for trees that store nicknames in the separate GEDCOM NICK field."
msgstr ""
"Setur GEDCOM NICK-gildið innan gæsalappa milli skírnarnafna og ættarnafns "
"(t.d. Martin \"Chalky\" White). Líkir eftir gamla webtrees-hegðuninni fyrir "
"tré sem geyma gælunöfn í sérstaka GEDCOM NICK-reitinn."

#: src/Configuration.php:422
msgid "Lowest level (e.g. parish)"
msgstr "Lægsta stig (t.d. sókn)"

