#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/form/inner-levels.phtml:27
msgid ""
"Specifies the number of levels in which the text is written along an arc. "
"Descendant arcs switch between arc text and rotated text automatically based "
"on available space."
msgstr ""
"Tilgreinir fjölda þrepa þar sem textinn er skrifaður eftir boga. Bogar "
"afkomenda skipta sjálfkrafa á milli bogatexta og snúins texta eftir tiltæku "
"plássi."

#: resources/views/modules/components/buttonbar/fullscreen-button.phtml:18
